title: What Do You Expect To Happen?, with Andy Frisella - MFCEO211
itunes:title: What Do You Expect To Happen?, with Andy Frisella - MFCEO211
description: I can tell you from personal experience most people get exactly what they expect. Not what they want. Not what they say they want. They don't get what they deserve.THEY GET WHAT THEY EXPECT. What is that supposed to mean? In this episode, I explain this concept, why it’s important and how to apply it.
